        "text_9UADmF": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Once you place an order through our website, you’ll receive an order confirmation email as well as regular email updates about your order status. If you opt in to SMS communication, you will also receive updates on your mobile phone. You can always log in to your BERO account and view your orders and their associated statuses and tracking number. If you have the Shop app, you can also track your order status in the app.</p>"
